title: Humsafar Lyrics – Alia Bhatt Version | Badrinath Ki Dulhania
text:
· Updated March 9, 2017 Humsafar Lyrics (Alia Bhatt Version) from Badrinath Ki Dulhania : A beautiful song sung by Alia Bhatt and Akhil Sachdeva, composed and written by Akhil Sachdeva. Humsafar : Alia Bhatt Version | Varun Dhawan | Akhil Sachdeva |"Badrinath Ki Dulhania" | T-Series Humsafar (Alia Bhatt Version) Lyrics 
Zaalima.. kyun hain dooriyan Hun tenu labban main kahan.. Das tenu labban main kahan.. 
Sun mere humsafar Kya tujhe itni si bhi khabar 
Sun mere humsafar Kya tujhe itni si bhi khabar Ki teri saansein chalti jidhar Rahungi bas wahin umrr bhar Rahungi bas wahin umrr bhar, haaye 
Muskurana bhi tujhi se seekha hai Dil lagane ka tu hi tareeka hai Aitbaar bhi tujhi se hota hai Aaun na hosh mein main kabhi Baahon mein hai teri zindagi 
Hai nahi tha pata Ki tujhe maan lungi Khuda Ki teri galiyon mein iss qadar Aaungi ab har pehar 
Kya tujhe itni si bhi khabar Ki teri saansein chalti jidhar Rahungi bas wahin umrr bhar Rahungi bas wahin umrr bhar, haaye 
Mere zaalima… Song: Humsafar (Alia Bhatt Version) Singers: Alia Bhatt, Akhil Sachdeva Lyrics: Akhil Sachdeva
